msgctxt "51188213-0-990"
msgid "Torn Note from Jessen"
msgstr ""

#: 21337012-0-961
msgctxt "21337012-0-961"
msgid "Firsthold is the key. Without Ayrenn's men holding the north, our Maormer allies will be free to move.\n\nBurning this little town is just a lark, yes. But it is for you, Lord Dagon. It's all for you."
msgstr ""

